name: Global Music Festival ZAMNA and Web3 Come Together for a New Era of Live Entertainment
description: Mid-ritual, the porcelain Saint of Transmission dissolves, yielding its form to the flow. Gritty circuits hum the gospel of the Web3 era, raining down streams of iridescent, kinetically charged data-currency. A cosmic transaction sanctified by sound.
